DONT RISK YOUR LIFE ON THAT SLIPPERY RIDGE OF DANGEROUS ROCKY UP-AND-DOWN.   
I MADE IT IN SAFETY CONDITIONS ( SUN, NO WIND, DRY ROCKS , NO CLOUDS OR FOG ).
